---
import IconArrow from '../IconArrow.astro';
---

<section class="pilot" id="pilot">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="eyebrow fade-up">Pilot</div>
    <h2 class="fade-up delay-1">30 days.<br>Your real users. <em>Your real data.</em></h2>
    <p class="pilot-modules fade-up delay-2">Transaction API · Viral Loop referral engine · Branded sets · Pan-African expansion</p>
    <p class="fade-up delay-2">We run AfriGlyph as a 30-day pilot. You measure dwell time and engagement during the base pilot. Share rate lands after WhatsApp Module activation. Organic acquisition lands after Viral Loop activation. The data makes the decision, not us.</p>

    <div class="pilot-boxes fade-up delay-2">
      <div class="pilot-box">
        <div class="pilot-box-num">30</div>
        <div class="pilot-box-label">Days. Enough time for meaningful usage data.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pilot-box">
        <div class="pilot-box-num">3</div>
        <div class="pilot-box-label">Metrics tracked. Dwell time, engagement; share rate after WhatsApp Module activation; organic acquisition after Viral Loop activation.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pilot-box">
        <div class="pilot-box-num">1</div>
        <div class="pilot-box-label">Integration. One API call in your success screen.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="pilot-price fade-up delay-3">30-day pilot — <strong>$1,000.</strong> Integration support included.</p>

    <div class="cta-stack fade-up delay-3">
      <a href="https://cal.com/afriglyph/demo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">
        Book your 10-minute demo
        <IconArrow />
      </a>
      <span class="cta-or">or</span>
      <a href="mailto:pilot@afriglyph.com" class="cta-email">pilot@afriglyph.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
